India’s Central Bank Raises Key Rate By a Quarter-Point to Quash Inflation

-- B y   K a r t i k   G o y a l
-- 
2011-03-17T06:32:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/india-s-central-bank-raises-key-rate-by-a-quarter-point-to-quash-inflation.html
  India ’s central bank raised its
benchmark repurchase rate by a quarter-percentage point to 6.75
percent, according to an e-mail statement from the monetary
authority. It also raised the reverse-repurchase rate by 25
basis points to 5.75 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
